:"mentions"},{"source":"recyADCa1iBgKqhkd","target":"recBZhqAvy5xhTNRn","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recyADCa1iBgKqhkd","target":"recLH8aOU6qflWJw8","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recyADCa1iBgKqhkd","target":"rectZ9CHWAIqw2hu2","label":"mentions"}],"verses":[{"id":"recpkTrzEzhimKNlN","ref":"Ps.83.1","text":"Keep not thou silence, O God: hold not thy peace, and be not still, O God."},{"id":"recWagsEcP8XD60DM","ref":"Ps.83.2","text":"For, lo, thine enemies make a tumult: and they that hate thee have lifted up the head."},{"id":"rec9hW3eqsfLbF6nb","ref":"Ps.83.3","text":"They have taken crafty counsel against thy people, and consulted against thy hidden ones."},{"id":"recDzyvTxz1LYUhiT","ref":"Ps.83.4","text":"They have said, Come, and let us cut them off from being a nation; that the name of Israel may be no more in remembrance."},{"id":"rec6lDQizTKdd76N3","ref":"Ps.83.5","text":"For they have consulted together with one consent: they are confederate against thee:"},{"id":"recCw2CGDJJKv3CfP","ref":"Ps.83.6","text":"The tabernacles of Edom, and the Ishmaelites; of Moab, and the Hagarenes;"},{"id":"rec8RTZBh3BqLQfoP","ref":"Ps.83.7","text":"Gebal, and Ammon, and Amalek; the Philistines with the inhabitants of Tyre;"},{"id":"recyUtZArCl1dhK3q","ref":"Ps.83.8","text":"Assur also is joined with them: they have holpen the children of Lot. Selah."}]}
